========================= Follow below steps ============================

1. First, set up the BigCommerce theme on Stencil.

2. Go to the templates > components > common ( folder or dir ).

3. Inside common create file for example: any-where.html

4. Write code inside ( any-where.html ) file , which are use many files.

5. Any file inside call like this :- {{> components/common/any-where }}
